snippet.title: QuantZ Official Trailer
snippet.description:
A trailer for QuantZ, a brain-twisting puzzle game by Gamerizon.

Get Quantz now on Steam, available on PC and Mac:
http://store.steampowered.com/app/37800/

You can also visit Gamerizon's YouTube page for more videos on our great games!
